00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,788
Episode 65

3
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:06,475
The Kang woman

4
00:01:06,475 --> 00:01:08,920
kept instigating and sowing discord among our family.

5
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:12,320
But who doesn't know

6
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,080
about the character of Big Madam?

7
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:15,568
Grandmother usually

8
00:01:15,568 --> 00:01:16,400
just pretended to be deaf and dumb.

9
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,640
She sometimes might say a few words, but that's it.

10
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:22,520
But, since she stuffed a concubine here,

11
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:26,080
it has agitated and angered grandmother.

12
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,520
She scolded her, took away her rights

13
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,720
and even punished her

14
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,965
by making her kneel at a place

15
00:01:30,965 --> 00:01:32,080
where people are moving about.

16
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,360
But the Big Madam

17
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,200
has been so competitive all her life.

18
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,560
If she could have just submitted a little,

19
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:42,510
that Lin woman would have been nothing

20
