in my father's eyes long time ago.

21
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:48,450
It was really too cruel for Big Madam.

22
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,000
That's why the evil woman found an opportunity.

23
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,120
No matter what,

24
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,240
she already has

25
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,680
a daughter-in-law and a grandchild.

26
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,400
She should be given appropriate respect,

27
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,400
at least.

28
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,000
Actually, if you're going to return to the root of everything,

29
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,200
I was the reason why

30
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,200
grandmother's life was endangered.

31
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:11,760
It was because she was too worried about me.

32
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:16,240
She always thinks for my sake.

33
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,200
At her age,

34
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,980
she should be enjoying the blessings

35
