from her children and grandchildren.

36
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:33,350
She should be living her life comfortably.

37
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,840
and shouldn't be worrying anymore.

38
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,280
But at her age,

39
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,720
she still has to suffer so much.

40
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,400
As her granddaughter,

41
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,440
my heart really aches for her.

42
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,560
I understand.

43
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,720
You have me.

44
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,000
You have me.

45
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,360
Don't worry.

46
