Grandmother loves me so much.

47
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,120
I feel so bad.

48
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,120
Miss,

49
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,400
Second Miss,

50
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,160
my good Miss,

51
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,520
you've been crying all day.

52
