Oh, my god. Oh, my god.

56
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:04,200
Why doesn't he just kill me now?

57
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,080
Miss.

58
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,360
That vile spawn,

59
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,347
