were good advice.

147
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,760
I actually didn't listen to them.

148
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,240
Since at the House of Wang, I've accompanied you.

149
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:42,640
Until you got married here and became the Big Madam.

150
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,200
