151
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,200
Big Madam,

152
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,300
don't cry anymore.

153
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,920
Let's go outside and take a stroll to relax your mind.

154
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,800
Look! How good the weather is.

155
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,840
Let's go.

156
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,640
Marquis,

157
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:10,600
Are you done with the salt taxation matters?

158
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,560
