159
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:19,760
Could it be that you returned to the capital without permission?

160
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,080
Your brother received

161
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,040
a letter from your sister-in-law.

162
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,520
After reading just two lines, he went to look for me.

163
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,880
Only then did I know that

164
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,040
a huge matter had happened to your family.

165
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:30,800
You,

166
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,320
and my older brother came back without permission?!

167
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,160
If this gets out,

168
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,240
it will be a grave crime!

169
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,320
You're anxious?

170
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:42,880
Of course, I'm worried about you!

171
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,320
Fortunately, the House of Wang got in trouble now.

172
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,320
No one would dare to spread this matter.

173
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,360
If people knew that

174
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,200
you returned to the capital without permission,

175
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:52,000
it will be hard to cover up this thing.

176
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,680
