177
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,800
I'm a capable man.

178
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:02,440
Before we left,

179
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:03,800
we've already informed Prince Huan.

180
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,240
Even if His Majesty learns of this,

181
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,840
