182
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,880
It's fine.

183
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,880
I learned that something bad happened to the family.

184
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:13,920
I learned that something bad happened to you.

185
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,320
I so wanted to put on wings

186
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,120
and fly back here!

187
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,880
I couldn't care about that much anymore.

188
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,880
I've caused you trouble.

189
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,240
On my way back here,

190
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,400
I kept thinking about one problem.

191
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,200
How come your sister-in-law

192
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,440
knew to write to your older brother,

193
