196
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,120
and too fast.

197
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:54,960
I didn't think that much.

198
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,240
No.

199
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,000
It's because you don't trust me at all.

200
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,360
You don't believe

201
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,080
