208
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:19,080
but I can't

209
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,000
risk yours.

210
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,080
How come your sister-in-law

211
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,000
risked the future of

212
